## Features

- 🚀 [Axum](https://github.com/tokio-rs/axum) web framework
- ⚡ [Tokio](https://tokio.rs/) async runtime
- 📝 Structured logging with [tracing](https://github.com/tokio-rs/tracing)
- 🐳 Docker and docker-compose ready
- 🔄 Hot reload with [cargo-watch](https://github.com/watchexec/cargo-watch)
- ✅ Health check endpoints (`/health`, `/ready`, `/live`)
- 🔒 CORS middleware configured
- 🗜️ Gzip compression
- ⏱️ Request timeout handling

## Prerequisites

- Rust {{rustVersion}} or higher
- Docker (optional)
- [cargo-watch](https://github.com/watchexec/cargo-watch) for hot reload (optional)

## Getting Started

### Run in development mode

```bash
# With hot reload
make dev

# Or without hot reload
make run
```

### Run tests

```bash
make test
```

### Build for production

```bash
make release
```

### Run with Docker

```bash
# Build image
make docker-build

# Run container
make docker-run

# Or use docker-compose
docker-compose up -d
```

