| `LOG_LEVEL` | `info` | Logging level (debug, info, warn, error) |
| `ENVIRONMENT` | `development` | Environment (development, staging, production) |
| `SERVICE_NAME` | `{{projectName}}` | Service name for tracing |
| `RUST_LOG` | `info` | Rust logging filter |

